Quickstrike:





Quickstrike looked at Vemonous. "Oh, well that's--" he began, finding 
that this was the Venomous Black Arachnia told him to let in, but 
seeing Stingtra in his arms spooked him. "Whoa! Ya can't bring her in 
here!" He backed up. She was Megatron's troops, and when she 
recovered, she would tell him that he was alive. "That's Stingtra, 
she's loyal t' Megatron!"
